    {
      "id": "3038d8c7_40aff7c7",
      "file_path": "jjb/cps/cps-ncmp-dmi-plugin.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "In cps-temporal, the maven artifacts are not required to be published which is not the case with ncmp-dmi-plugins. So, we should use 'gerrit-maven-merge' and 'gerrit-maven-stage' to publish both maven artifacts and docker images. CPS-temporal initially configured these jobs as below.\n\n      - gerrit-maven-merge\n      - gerrit-maven-stage:\n          sign-artifacts: true\n          build-node: centos7-docker-8c-8g\n          maven-versions-plugin: true\n\nThe configuration has been taken from https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/ci-management/+/118006/17/jjb/cps/cps-cps-temporal.yaml change",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7680,
        "name": "Renu Kumari",
        "display_name": "Renu Kumari",
        "email": "kashi.renu@gmail.com",
        "username": "renukumari"
      },
      "updated": "2021-05-27 18:38:32.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "d34f6d92_35ecf898",
      "file_path": "jjb/cps/cps-ncmp-dmi-plugin.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 23,
      "message": "It is one of the required parameters for 'gerrit-maven-merge'. As per the description, it is required to pull the credentials from the settings.xml\n\nhttps://github.com/lfit/releng-global-jjb/blob/master/docs/jjb/lf-maven-jobs.rst",
